MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2007-1828. Evans v. Mazda Motors of Am., Inc.

Scioto App. No. 06CA3118, 2007-Ohio-4622. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary-appeal and claimed appeal of right. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
